race.comment: Some in-form gallopers come together in an intriguing contest. DIAMOND EPIC (2) built on her impressive record last time out when she came with a well-timed run to score over this distance at the Sunshine Coast. Goes up 2kgs in a similar race. Sure to run her usual honest race. REZONE (3) made it three wins from as many runs this prep when she just got home over the mile here two weeks ago. Dug deep that day in a run that suggested 1800m is the next step. Big chance again. ECLAIR AWESOME (6) didn't have everything go right last start when 2.3 lengths behind REZONE. Won at 1870m last prep so this looks a nice race for her. LUTON HOO (7) next elect off of two straight second placings.
